= About =

Major-mode for editing web templates aka HTML documents embedding parts (CSS, JavaScript) and blocks (php, jsp, asp, django, twig, erb, etc).
Template engine compatibility : PHP, JSP, ASP / ASP.NET AJAX (Atlas), Django / Twig / Jinja(2) / ErlyDTL (Zotonic), ERB, FreeMarker, Velocity, Cheetah, Smarty, CTemplate / Mustache / Hapax / Handlebars / ember.js, Blade (laravel), Knockoutjs, Go Template (Revel), Razor/Play, Dust, Closure (soy), underscore.js

= Home page =

http://web-mode.org/

